queries.sql: SELECT u.id AS user_id, u.name AS nama, u.email, SUM(COALESCE(iz_jml,0)) AS izin_total, SUM(COALESCE(ct_jml,0)) AS cuti_total FROM karyawan k JOIN users u ON u.id = k.user_id LEFT JOIN ( SELECT i.karyawan_id, COUNT(*) iz_jml FROM izin i WHERE i.tgl_mulai BETWEEN '2025-12-01' AND '2025-12-31' GROUP BY i.karyawan_id ) iz ON iz.karyawan_id = k.id LEFT JOIN ( SELECT c.karyawan_id, COUNT(*) ct_jml FROM cuti c WHERE c.tgl_mulai BETWEEN '2025-12-01' AND '2025-12-31' GROUP BY c.karyawan_id ) ct ON ct.karyawan_id = k.id GROUP BY u.id, u.name, u.email ORDER BY u.name ASC
